Subject: Re: [VB] 67 Spring Plates, 4 lug brakes, and early front

>Are the spring plates the same on the '67 as my '60?

Yes, should be.

>What can I do to convert these to 5 lug (without wheel adapters)?

Maybe THING drums....they're wide 5. Or you could buy a set of 
aftermarket drums for a later bug that are drilled for 5-lug. Or you 
could bolt on an early 5-lug bug drum using a spacer to make it fit.

